		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/11/19/today-in-small-business-pastry-coffee-and-cats/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Pastry, Coffee and Cats" data-description="&quot;Vape&quot; beats &quot;slacktivism.&quot; A business owner in Washington state says FEMA&#039;s red tape is forcing her out of business. And why businesses need to change the way they accept payments.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Economy</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Target&#8217;s <a href="//www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-11-19/target-third-quarter-profit-tops-estimates-after-sales-recover.html">profit tops estimates</a>.</li>
<li>A closely watched <a href="//www.calculatedriskblog.com/2014/11/ata-trucking-index-increased-05-in.html">trucking-activity index</a> rose in October.</li>
<li>Home builder <a href="//247wallst.com/housing/2014/11/18/homebuilder-confidence-regains-upward-trend-in-november/?u">confidence regained</a> its upward trend in November.</li>
<li>Wholesale inflation rises <a href="//usat.ly/1qS1qId">even as</a> gas costs fall.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Start-Up</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A <a href="//www.washingtoncitypaper.com/blogs/citydesk/2014/11/18/d-c-s-cat-cafe-may-have-a-5-to-7-cover-charge/">new cafe</a> in Washington, D.C., offers pastry, coffee and cats.</li>
<li>These are the <a href="//www.cnbc.com/id/102186254">best places</a> in the world to start a business.</li>
<li>A start-up offers<a href="//money.cnn.com/2014/11/18/smallbusiness/startup-alfred-butler/index.html"> butler service</a> for the 99 percent.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Cash Flow</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A webinar explains why businesses need <a href="//info.kabbage.com/mobile-payments-webinar">to change the way</a> they accept payments.</li>
<li>A small-business owner <a href="//www.wjhl.com/story/27406840/small-business-owner-loses-37k-thanks-to-identity-thief">loses $37,000</a> to an identity thief.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span id="more-90342"></span><br />
<strong>Finance</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The Securities and Exchange Commission&#8217;s long delay approving <a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com//2014/11/18/s-e-c-s-delay-on-crowdfunding-may-just-save-it-2/">crowdfunding rules</a> may actually save crowdfunding.</li>
<li>Ami Kassar and Entrepreneur have createdÂ <a href="//www.entrepreneur.com/bestbanks/about">a tool to help small businesses</a> find banks that are lending to small businesses.</li>
<li>A company that offers tools <a href="//techcrunch.com/2014/11/18/breezeworks-raises-5-million-for-tools-that-let-service-pros-run-their-business-from-their-smartphone/">to help service companies</a> run their businesses from their smartphones raises $5 million.</li>
<li>A start-up that serves as a <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/teespring-2014-11?nr_email_referer=1&amp;utm_source=Sailthru&amp;utm_medium=email&amp;utm_content=TechSelect">Kickstarter for T-shirt companies</a> has turned 10 people into millionaires.</li>
<li>Here&#8217;s why <a href="//www.divestopedia.com/2/5853/sale-process/employee-agreements/the-problems-with-esops">employee-stock-ownership plans</a> are not for everyone.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Employees</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Peter Thiel <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/peter-thiel-loves-this-interview-question-2014-11">loves this</a> job interview question: &#8220;Tell me something that&#8217;s true, that almost nobody agrees with you on.&#8221;</li>
<li>According to a Duke behavioral scientist, our <a href="https://www.freelancersunion.org/blog/2014/11/17/two-most-productive-hours-day/?">most productive</a> hours are right after we wake up.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Taxes</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>It&#8217;s <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/11/19/business/in-congress-crunch-time-for-dubious-tax-breaks.html">crunchtime for tax breaks</a> in Congress.</li>
<li>Here are five ways to <a href="//www.rootsofwealth.com/irs-scam-phone-calls-on-the-rise?ut">detect</a> that a phone call allegedly from the Internal Revenue Service really isn&#8217;t.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Business Travel</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A passenger gets stuck with a <a href="//blogs.wsj.com/digits/2014/11/18/passenger-stuck-with-1171-wi-fi-bill-on-singapore-airlines-flight/">$1,171 Wi-Fi bill</a> on Singapore Airlines.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the Country</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A business owner in Washington state says FEMA&#8217;s red tape <a href="//www.king5.com/story/news/local/2014/11/17/stanwood-business-fema/19204763/">is forcing her out</a> of business.</li>
<li>Oregon employers <a href="//www.foxbusiness.com/markets/2014/11/18/oregon-employers-hired-big-time-this-fall-october-figures-show-00-new-jobs/">have been hiring</a> this fall.</li>
<li>A truck <a href="//www.latimes.com/business/la-fi-truckers-strike-20141117-story.html">driver strike</a> at the twin ports of Los Angeles and Long Beach is expanding.</li>
<li>After a long, troubled history, city <a href="//www.brooklynpaper.com/stories/37/47/dtg-goldenrod-evicted-2014-11-21-bk_37_47.html">marshals seize</a> what may be the oldest bar in Brooklyn.</li>
<li>In Newark, N.J., a <a href="//www.nj.com/essex/index.ssf/2014/11/a_road_less_traveled_is_angering_newark_business_owners.html">new bike lane</a> has caused a drop in business for many shops.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Around the World</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>âVapeâ is <a href="//www.nydailynews.com/life-style/vape-named-2014-oxford-dictionaries-word-year-article-1.2014867">the Oxford dictionaryâs</a> word of the year.</li>
<li>Appleâs new UnionPay deal could <a href="//qz.com/297501/apples-new-unionpay-deal-could-pave-the-way-for-apple-pay-in-china/">pave the way</a> for Apple Pay in China.</li>
<li>Japanâs gross domestic product may be falling but <a href="//info.crunchbase.com/2014/11/japans-gdp-falls-but-venture-deals-are-on-the-rise/">venture deals</a> are on the rise.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Retail</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A dining writer <a href="//nrn.com/amexfsvoice/noise-restaurants-disconnect-customers?ut">recently asked his readers</a> how they feel about restaurant noise. Nearly 80 percent said, âLoathe it.â</li>
<li>Pizza Hut is <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/11/19/business/media/in-overhaul-pizza-hut-tries-adventurous-menu-offerings-and-a-dash-of-irreverence.html">getting an overhaul</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Law</strong></p>
<ul>
